data.title: Love that Starbucks in such a great mini-mall
data.text: This is a nice location for a Starbucks. I love to do mobile orders, park in the :20 minutes space and run in and pick up my Skinny Vanilla Latte and Oatmeal. The general parking can be tight during busy times due to the Trader Joes and other attractions.

data.title: Friendly service, could use more tables
data.text: The baristas are very nice and helpful, especially when they run out of chocolate milk! They seem like they have a lot of open space where there could be more tables, but I have a feeling they need that space for the long lines. There are outside tables too, but all the tables always seem to be full.

data.title: Friendly Place
data.text: 's standard Starbucks - but nice.  Can have a problem finding parking since Trader Joes is there and parking lot can be very busy.

data.title: Typically busy and consistently good
data.text: This Starbucks is in a busy location and I visited it several times during a visit to Sunnyvale.  It is consistent with most of the other Starbucks I have visited which is a positive thing.  When you go there you know what you're getting.

data.title: Meet @ Starbucks
data.text: This Starbucks is located at the intersection of Stevens Crekk Blvd. and De Anza Blvd. close to companies and shops.  The place has outside seating although it's a little noisy and a lot of traffic.  The place is usually crowded and there's a little wait to get your coffee.  Sometimes, it's difficult to find parking.

data.title: Had a non-coffee drink.
data.text: Had my first in a long time, a very good cold non-coffee drink, the double chocolate chip frappuccino. Seated out doors to meet with friends and relatives.

data.title: Great Sbux in shopping mall!
data.text:
This is a nicely designed, fast moving Sbux with good service. It is a decent sized one as well, so likelihood of getting a seat is good as well. There are a few large communal tables as well as a bar and a bunch of smaller tables.

The baristas work the line nicely and get drinks made quickly. The noise level of the place is a little high if you are trying to concentrate, but overall a great SBUX!
